<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            background-image: url("/background3.jpg");
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: 100%;
        }
        h1 {
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            -webkit-text-stroke: 1px blue;
        }
        .container1 {
            position: fixed;
            left: 50px;
            top: 150px;
            color: white;
        }
        .container2 {
            position: fixed;
            left: 300px;
            top: 150px;
            color: white;
            width: 300px;
            text-align: justify;
            text-justify: inter-word;
        }
        .video {
            position: fixed;
            left: 700px;
            top: 150px;
            color: white;
            width: 300px;
            text-align: justify;
            text-justify: inter-word;
        }
        .wanttogo {
            position: fixed;
            left: 30px;
            top: 470px;
        }
        #my {
            zoom: 110%;
        }
    </style>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Mount Cook</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    <div class="container">
        <h1><%= actualName %></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="container1">
        <img id="image" src="/cook.png" width="193" height="300">
    </div>
    <div class="container2">
        Soaring as New Zealand's highest peak, Aoraki / Mount Cook anchors the Southern Alps with its jagged, glaciated summit. Sacred to the Ngāi Tahu people, this alpine giant lies within a Dark Sky Reserve and was a training ground for Sir Edmund Hillary. Surrounded by turquoise lakes and ancient ice, it remains a premier destination for adventurers seeking a raw, breathtaking wilderness experience amidst the dramatic landscapes of the South Island.
    <div class="wanttogo">
        <form method="POST" action="/destination/cook/add">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-secondary ml-3">Add to Want-to-Go List</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div class="video">
       <iframe width="560" height="315" 
    src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-a-mo0dYekw?si=e6cXZ1OXqifhCO9b"
    title="YouTube video player" 
    frameborder="0" 
    allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" 
    allowfullscreen>
</iframe>
    </div>

</body>

</html>